              <Source_ID>2000052374/Polytechnisch woordenboek En-Ne (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指含量為3:1及1:1的銅鎳合金板、鑄塊和彈丸。可用於在黃銅中添加鎳。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
